{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Join Our Discord!</h2><br><br>Aquium aims to create a unique opportunity for players to create a beautiful aquarium in a calming and relaxing world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create your own Aquarium!</h2>Use a diverse collection of various objects from rocks &amp; plants to fantasy buildings to craft a special aquarium for your fishes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746620/extras/ScreenShot00015.png?t=1716200689\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Catch wild fishes!</h2>Aquium allows you to catch fishes in the world --both realistic and fantastical-- to add them to your customized aquarium!<br>You may also sell the fish to obtain gold, which can be used to buy customization options and upgrade your gear.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746620/extras/ScreenShot00016.png?t=1716200689\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize &amp; buy your ship!</h2>You can buy new ships of different speeds, storage sizes, etc., and customize them to your liking!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2746620/extras/ScreenShot00020.png?t=1716200689\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Upgrade your fishing gear!</h2>Use gold to upgrade your own fishing gear, which may assist increasing in the number of fish to be caught at once, increasing rarity percentages, etc.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Please Note:</h2>Aquium is not an aquarium or fishing simulation experience by any means and is meant for casual play. If you are looking for aspects like pH levels, water temperature, water types, etc., please note that this game will not include these aspects.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hobbyist Fisher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2746620/cd8648d102551e0e08ae998dda9bfbb40b0d007b.jpg"},{"name":"Amateur Fisher","path":"https://cdn.akamai